'''''ango''''' (plural ''angwi'') is a noun meaning "[[Snakes|snake]]" in [[Quenya]].<ref name=Ety349>{{LR|Etymologies}}, p. 349</ref>
==Etymology==
It is derived from the [[Elvish]] [[Sundocarme|root]] [[ANGWA|ANGWA/ANGU]].<ref name=Ety349/>
==See also==
*[[Quenya]] ''[[lókë]]''

==Cognates==
